title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 11 - new beta available
description:
In this video we will look at the latest beta version which has been released for the already released Sim Update 11. Asobo is working hard on to resolve issues reported by simmers and based on this they decided to continue to work using the existing beta. Based on this it looks like it will be a more a hotfix instead of a full new release.
